nodes.text: The Cargo Sky was a Wayfarer-class medium transport that was part of Senator Bail Organa's resistance movement During the blockade of the planet Ibaar, Organa ordered Cargo Sky and Cargo Comet to be loaded with supplies and military equipment and to deliver it to the rebel network operating there.

While Bail Organa's adoptive daughter, Princess Leia Organa, oversaw Cargo Comet and Cargo Sky being loaded with the cargo in Sanctuary Coast Starport on Alderaan, six agents from the Imperial Security Bureau and Imperial Office of Customs arrived at the landing bay to inspect the shipment, and subsequently ordered licenses and manifests for review.
